OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with largely clear skies,
OL,7,Falthough a veil of high cloud will
OL,8,Fmove over at times. Odd shower in the
OL,9,Ffar west possible. A patchy rural
OL,10,Ffrost is possible in the coldest spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAnother largely dry day with
OL,13,Fhazy sunshine. After a chilly start,
OL,14,Fit will warm up through the day,
OL,15,Fthough still holding onto brisk winds
OL,16,Fearly on.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
