OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMore
OL,6,Fhumid on Friday with the risk of
OL,7,Fthunderstorms by the afternoon.
OL,8,FTurning increasingly cloudy through
OL,9,Fthe weekend with an increasing risk of
OL,10,Fheavy showers, possibly thundery.
